{
    "poem_title": "LA CHAMBRE DE JUSTICE",
    "author": "",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1709-1775",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Toi dont le redoutable Alcée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Suivait les transports et la voix,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Muse, viens peindre à ma pensée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "La France réduite aux abois.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Je me livre à ta violence ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "C'est trop, dans un lâche silence,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Nourrir d'inutiles douleurs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Je vais, dans l'ardeur qui m'enflamme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Flétrir le tribunal infâme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Qui met le comble à nos malheurs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Toi dont le redoutable Alcée\nSuivait les transports et la voix,\nMuse, viens peindre à ma pensée\nLa France réduite aux abois.\nJe me livre à ta violence ;\nC'est trop, dans un lâche silence,\nNourrir d'inutiles douleurs.\nJe vais, dans l'ardeur qui m'enflamme,\nFlétrir le tribunal infâme\nQui met le comble à nos malheurs."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Une tyrannique industrie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Épuise aujourd'hui son savoir ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Son implacable barbarie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Se mesure sur son pouvoir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Le délateur, monstre exécrable,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Est orné d'un titre honorable,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "A la honte de notre nom ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "L'esclave fait trembler son maître ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Enfin nous allons voir renaître",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Les temps de Claude et de Néron.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Une tyrannique industrie\nÉpuise aujourd'hui son savoir ;\nSon implacable barbarie\nSe mesure sur son pouvoir.\nLe délateur, monstre exécrable,\nEst orné d'un titre honorable,\nA la honte de notre nom ;\nL'esclave fait trembler son maître ;\nEnfin nous allons voir renaître\nLes temps de Claude et de Néron."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "En vain l'Auteur de la nature",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "S'est réservé le fond des cœurs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Si l'orgueilleuse créature",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Ose en sonder les profondeurs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Une ordonnance criminelle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Veut qu'en public chacun révèle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Les opprobres de sa maison ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Et, pour couronner l'entreprise,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "On fait d'un pays de franchise",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Une immense et vaste prison.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "En vain l'Auteur de la nature\nS'est réservé le fond des cœurs,\nSi l'orgueilleuse créature\nOse en sonder les profondeurs.\nUne ordonnance criminelle\nVeut qu'en public chacun révèle\nLes opprobres de sa maison ;\nEt, pour couronner l'entreprise,\nOn fait d'un pays de franchise\nUne immense et vaste prison."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Quel gouffre sous mes pas s'entr'ouvre !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Quels spectres me glacent d'effroi !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "L'enfer ténébreux se découvre :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "C'est Tysiphone, je la voi.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "La Terreur, l'Envie, et la Rage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Guident son funeste passage :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Des foudres partent de ses yeux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Elle tient dans ses mains perfides",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Un tas de glaives homicides",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Dont elle arme des furieux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quel gouffre sous mes pas s'entr'ouvre !\nQuels spectres me glacent d'effroi !\nL'enfer ténébreux se découvre :\nC'est Tysiphone, je la voi.\nLa Terreur, l'Envie, et la Rage,\nGuident son funeste passage :\nDes foudres partent de ses yeux ;\nElle tient dans ses mains perfides\nUn tas de glaives homicides\nDont elle arme des furieux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Déjà la troupe meurtrière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Commence ses sanglants exploits ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Elle ouvre l'affreuse carrière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Par le renversement des lois.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Contre la force et l'imposture",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "La foi, la candeur, la droiture,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Sont des asiles impuissants.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Tout cède à l'horrible tempête ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "S'il tombe une coupable tête,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "On égorge mille innocents.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Déjà la troupe meurtrière\nCommence ses sanglants exploits ;\nElle ouvre l'affreuse carrière\nPar le renversement des lois.\nContre la force et l'imposture\nLa foi, la candeur, la droiture,\nSont des asiles impuissants.\nTout cède à l'horrible tempête ;\nS'il tombe une coupable tête,\nOn égorge mille innocents."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Tel, sortant du mont de Sicile,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Un torrent de soufre enflammé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Engloutit un terrain fertile",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Et son habitant alarmé ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Tel un loup, fumant de carnage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Enveloppe dans son ravage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Les bergers avec les troupeaux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Telle était, moins terrible encore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "La fatale boîte où Pandore",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Cachait à nos veux tous les maux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tel, sortant du mont de Sicile,\nUn torrent de soufre enflammé\nEngloutit un terrain fertile\nEt son habitant alarmé ;\nTel un loup, fumant de carnage,\nEnveloppe dans son ravage\nLes bergers avec les troupeaux ;\nTelle était, moins terrible encore,\nLa fatale boîte où Pandore\nCachait à nos veux tous les maux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Dans cet odieux parallèle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Ne rencontrez-vous pas vos traits,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Magistrats d'un nouveau modèle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Que l'enfer en courroux a faits ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Vils partisans de la Fortune,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Que le cri du faible importune,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Par qui les bons sont abattus,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Chez qui la Cruauté farouche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Les Préjugés au regard louche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Tiennent la place des Vertus ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dans cet odieux parallèle\nNe rencontrez-vous pas vos traits,\nMagistrats d'un nouveau modèle,\nQue l'enfer en courroux a faits ;\nVils partisans de la Fortune,\nQue le cri du faible importune,\nPar qui les bons sont abattus,\nChez qui la Cruauté farouche,\nLes Préjugés au regard louche,\nTiennent la place des Vertus ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Nous périssons : tout se dérange ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Tous les états sont confondus.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Partout règne un désordre étrange :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "On ne voit qu'hommes éperdus ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Leurs cœurs sont fermés à la joie ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Leurs biens vont devenir la proie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "De leurs ennemis triomphants.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "O désespoir ! notre patrie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "N'est plus qu'une mère en furie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Qui met en pièces ses enfants.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nous périssons : tout se dérange ;\nTous les états sont confondus.\nPartout règne un désordre étrange :\nOn ne voit qu'hommes éperdus ;\nLeurs cœurs sont fermés à la joie ;\nLeurs biens vont devenir la proie\nDe leurs ennemis triomphants.\nO désespoir ! notre patrie\nN'est plus qu'une mère en furie\nQui met en pièces ses enfants."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Je sens que mes craintes redoublent ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "Le ciel s'obstine à nous punir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "Que d'objets affligeants me troublent !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "Je lis dans le sombre avenir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 85,
                    "line_text": "Bientôt les guerres intestines,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 86,
                    "line_text": "Les massacres, et les rapines,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 87,
                    "line_text": "Deviendront les jeux des mortels.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 88,
                    "line_text": "On souillera le sanctuaire :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 89,
                    "line_text": "Les dieux d'une terre étrangère",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 90,
                    "line_text": "Vont déshonorer nos autels.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je sens que mes craintes redoublent ;\nLe ciel s'obstine à nous punir.\nQue d'objets affligeants me troublent !\nJe lis dans le sombre avenir.\nBientôt les guerres intestines,\nLes massacres, et les rapines,\nDeviendront les jeux des mortels.\nOn souillera le sanctuaire :\nLes dieux d'une terre étrangère\nVont déshonorer nos autels."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 91,
                    "line_text": "Vieille erreur, respect chimérique,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 92,
                    "line_text": "Sortez de nos cœurs mutinés ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 93,
                    "line_text": "Chassons le sommeil léthargique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
